Package com.slasherstats.model

Class HorrorMovieSQL

java.lang.Object
com.slasherstats.model.HorrorMovieSQL
@Entity public class HorrorMovieSQL extends Object
Entity class representing a horror movie record stored in the SQL database. This class is mapped to the horror_movies table using JPA annotations.
